  <brief_title>Diffusion of Local Anesthetic After Median Nerve Block</brief_title>
  <acronym>Echoalr</acronym>
  <official_title>Can Ultrasound Predict Success of Median Nerve Block? Relationship Between Diffusion of Local Anesthetic and Effectiveness of a Nerve Block</official_title>
  <sponsors>
